      "content": "wait sorry what do you mean by a \"goblin's game of chance\"? i'm just trying to understand the legal side of it. can you just explain the specific steps of how the money gets moved from my account to the escrow agent and then to the seller? i just want to make sure i don't lose my deposit if something goes wrong.",
